track_notes: This is a summit that lessable people can reach, you just need a car that can go on forest road.The landscape is wonderfull; it is a must.The road leads on summit and it is a good place for radio.
This is not the shortest path to go on the 2 summits. To make it shorter you must park in between the summits at the Baisse de Ournes. 4 Wheel drive is best
Since the Alex storm, it must be difficult to start from this place. get enquiry
